Cebbo Kameran
<span class="padding-top"><br></span><h3>Hur fungerar kameran?</h3><span class="padding-bottom"><br></span>
<span class="padding-top"><br></span><p>Kamera ikonen kan du hitta nere i vänstra hörnet av din skärm. Efter du klickar där är du redo att ta bilder. Photo taking is easy, just press the red button! The photos taken (max. 5) are saved in the menu below the camera. You can also replace the saved photos with the ones you like the best. Just bare in mind that the saved photos are not permanent but disappear when reloading the client. The only way to keep the photos to yourself is converting them into wall-item furnis.</p><span class="padding-bottom"><br></span>
<span class="padding-top"><br></span><h3>Kan alla använda kameran?</h3><span class="padding-bottom"><br></span>
<span class="padding-top"><br></span><p>Ja, alla kan använda kameran och det är helt gratis. Man kan dock bli avstängd om man skulle missbruka kameran.</p><span class="padding-bottom"><br></span>
<span class="padding-top"><br></span><h3>Blir bilderna kontrollerade?</h3><span class="padding-bottom"><br></span>
<span class="padding-top"><br></span><p>Ja, bilderna blir kontrollerade på grund utav säkerhetsskäl.</p><span class="padding-bottom"><br></span>
<span class="padding-top"><br></span><h3>Varför syns inte bubblorna i bilerna?</h3><span class="padding-bottom"><br></span>
<span class="padding-top"><br></span><p>Har du någonsin sett ett pratande photo i verkligheten? inte vi heller.</p><span class="padding-bottom"><br></span>
<span class="padding-top"><br></span><h3>What about zoom, filters, frames, effects and other cool features?</h3><span class="padding-bottom"><br></span>
<span class="padding-top"><br></span><p>We're working really hard to get more awesome features to go with the camera. Hopefully cool stuff will be at your reach very soon!</p><span class="padding-bottom"><br></span>